entry.value: UPDATE norma.device_element_uses SET crop_counts_by_score = ${crop_counts_by_score}::json WHERE id = ${id}::uuid

UPDATE norma.device_element_uses SET travel_distance_meter = odometer_at_end_time - odometer_at_start_time, elapsed_time_seconds = extract(epoch from end_time) - extract(epoch from start_time) WHERE id = ${id}::uuid

SELECT avg(odometer_meter) AS odometer FROM stout.machine_telematics_data WHERE machine_name = ${machine_name} AND organization_id = ${organization_id}::uuid AND ts > ${send_time}::timestamptz - '1 second'::interval AND ts < ${send_time}::timestamptz + '1 second'::interval

SELECT avg(odometer_meter) AS odometer FROM stout.machine_telematics_data WHERE machine_name = ${machine_name} AND organization_id = ${organization_id}::uuid AND ts > ${start_time}::timestamptz - '1 second'::interval AND ts < ${start_time}::timestamptz + '1 second'::interval
